<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN325">
      <lg type="edition" style="pūṭṭuvil">
<l>kaḷiṟunī ṟāṭiya viṭunila maruṅkiṉ</l>
<l>vampap perumpeyal varaintucorin tiṟanteṉak</l>
<l>kuḻikoḷ ciṉṉīr kurāa luṇṭaliṟ</l>
<l>cēṟukiḷait tiṭṭa kaluḻkaṇ ṇūṟaṉ</l>
<l>muṟaiyi ṉuṇṇu niṟaiyā vāḻkkai</l>
<l>muḷavumāt tolaicciya muḻucco lāṭava</l>
<l>ruṭumpiḻu taṟutta voṭuṅkāḻp paṭalaic</l>
<l>cīṟiṉ muṉṟiṟ kūṟucey tiṭumār</l>
<l>koḷḷi vaitta koḻuniṇa nāṟṟam</l>
<l>maṟukuṭaṉ kamaḻu matukai maṉṟat</l>
<l>talantalai yiratti yalaṅkupaṭu nīḻaṟ</l>
<l>kayantalaic ciṟāar kaṇaiviḷai yāṭu</l>
<l>marumiḷai yirukkai yatuvē veṉvēl</l>
<l>vēntutalai variṉun tāṅkum</l>
<l>tāṅkā vīkai neṭuntakai yūrē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>With a livelihood that is insufficient, where [people] drink in turn</l>
<l>of what oozes from the murky spot that is dug in the mud,</l>
<l>as the tawny cow had drunk the little water held by the pit,</l>
<l>because the great new rains have traversed [the place], pouring to a limited amount</l>
<l>on the loose ground where elephant bulls bathe in the dust,</l>
<l>it is a seat with an enclosure difficult [to cross],</l>
<l>where soft-headed boys play with arrows</l>
<l>in the swaying shade that falls from the fig tree with a sickly crown,</l>
<l>on the strong village common where all the streets are fragrant</l>
<l>of the scent of rich fat to which a fire brand is put</l>
<l>in order to make shares, in the front yard of the small house</l>
<l>shaded by the core of the Oṭum tree when men of whole word(?)</l>
<l>cut off the fat of an iguana, [men] who had killed a porcupine,</l>
<l>the village of the paragon of unhalting generosity</l>
<l>who will uphold even when the king with victorious spear come at [him].</l>
</lg>
    </div>
